I've hit someone.

101
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,879
Come quickly.

102
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,480
Hurry.

103
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,560
What's going on?

104
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,040
Don't speak.

105
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,879
Don't speak.

106
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:29,920
Did I hit someone?

107
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,080
Don't hurt Qinian.

108
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:35,960
Listen.

109
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,480
As long as you behave,

110
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,679
I promise she'll be fine.

111
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,840
Get it?

112
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,120
Come sit here.

113
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,039
Drive.

114
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,919
Remember.

115
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:49,399
You hit someone with your car.

116
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,559
Make the confession

117
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,879
and your daughter will be fine.

118
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,679
Got it?

119
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,639
Got it?

120
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,480
Yeah.

